### 新增一条用户记录（关联作品ID）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjectId": 1,
  "recordStatus": "WATCHED",
  "scoreValue": 48,
  "recordYear": 2024,
  "recordQuarter": "Q1",
  "note": "补番"
}

### 查询全部用户记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/records

### 按状态查询用户记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/records?status=WATCHED

### 按 id 查询用户记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/records/2

### 按 id 更新用户记录（改成关联作品ID）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/records/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjectId": 1,
  "recordStatus": "WATCHED",
  "scoreValue": 49,
  "recordYear": 2024,
  "recordQuarter": "Q2",
  "note": "更新后的备注"
}

### 删除一条用户记录
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/records/1

### 非法新增：缺少标题并且季度非法
POST http://localhost:8080/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjectTitle": "",
  "recordStatus": "WATCHED",
  "scoreValue": 48,
  "recordYear": 2024,
  "recordQuarter": "Q5",
  "note": "这是一条非法请求"
}